Overseeing the operations and compliance of this Florida Limited Liability Company is Barberousse, Monica C, who serves as the registered agent. He is based at the same address as the company's principal address.

The guiding force behind this is Barberousse, Monica C from Miami FL, holding the position of Manager.

The company does not have an FEI/EIN number. Additionally, since it is a fresh entrant in the business landscape, the company has not filed any annual reports as of its last update.
